WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.066 --> 00:00:02.966
You really have some nerve!

2
00:00:06.900 --> 00:00:09.900
Your Majesty, what are you doing here?

3
00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:13.600
Those despicable people, one plays the role of the good cop, the other the bad cop.

4
00:00:13.933 --> 00:00:16.366
It’s a pity they don’t form a theater troupe.

5
00:00:17.533 --> 00:00:18.300
Your Majesty.

6
00:00:18.300 --> 00:00:20.533
This is a dragon bone soup I personally made for you.

7
00:00:20.533 --> 00:00:23.366
Please try it. You’ve worked hard.

8
00:00:23.700 --> 00:00:25.133
The pot you’ve been discussing.

9
00:00:25.133 --> 00:00:27.600
This Fanghua tea has been given to you for a year.

10
00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:28.800
How does it taste?

11
00:00:28.800 --> 00:00:34.633
I added a bit of Soul-shattering Powder to it today.

12
00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:41.300
In the past life, after I was poisoned by Consort Yang,

13
00:00:41.366 --> 00:00:43.066
Prince Duan invaded the palace.

14
00:00:43.266 --> 00:00:44.866
They should have dealt with him.

15
00:00:44.900 --> 00:00:48.100
If it weren’t for the Empress’s decisive action killing Consort Yin,

16
00:00:48.266 --> 00:00:51.366
Shan Town might have fallen into the hands of these vile lovers.

17
00:00:51.800 --> 00:00:53.866
Why is this despicable emperor looking at me?

18
00:00:54.133 --> 00:00:56.033
Is he going to make a move against me?

19
00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:02.566
Speak up, what’s all this commotion about?

20
00:01:02.733 --> 00:01:04.000
If I hadn’t come,

21
00:01:04.366 --> 00:01:06.766
the harem would have been in chaos.
